{"tid":702612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私樓地盤工人追討欠薪 坐出危險位置","createTime":"2018-06-15T04:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T07:17:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"603886cce1a754663c0d31f3a0adb5ad41bb02d2","tid":702612,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529033347_bdfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529033347_bdfb.jpg&h=73623cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時許，葵涌興芳路178號一個私人樓宇地盤，有約40名工人在地盤內拉起橫額追討欠薪，橫額寫上「有汗出冇糧出」，其間一名工人情緒激動，走到約4層樓高的平台，坐在危險位置。警方接報到場，通知消防協助，在地面張開救生氣墊戒備。危坐工人經半小時游說後，終被勸服，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，40名工人被二判拖欠三個月人工，總數約400萬元，但二判聲稱大判未有支付足夠金錢，而大判則聲稱已給錢二判。警方調查後，列糾紛處理，轉交勞工處調停。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180615/58320678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320678&d=zojaX6QYh3L6vsaSyb2PlviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d3382009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320678&h=95d90695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180615/58320678</a>"},{"pid":"f070d4a892a4255352e2b039117e25f15cfffde9","tid":702612,"uid":75686,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"603886cce1a754663c0d31f3a0adb5ad41bb02d2","tid":702612,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529033347_bdfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529033347_bdfb.jpg&h=73623cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時許，葵涌興芳路1